data.description: This is an adorable well maintained ranch style home with (over 2700 sq/ft total finish)  a semi private feel back yard with no neighbors directly behind.  This lovely home is located in a convenient location close to freeway access - as soon as the bridge is finished.  The kitchen has beautiful cream cabinets offset by darker tiered kitchen island flattering finish of  backsplash and stunning granite countertops.  The trim through out the home is the beautiful cream trim and cream doors that lends calming feeling of coziness to the home.   One of the rooms has charming French glass doors to allow light to flow in, can be used for an office/or 3rd bedroom on main floor. The bathrooms all boast lovely upgrades of the granite countertops and tile floors.  The generous sized Master Suite has a bathroom with soaking tub /shower with lovely upgraded tile shower walls .   Enormous finished basement feels like the main floor with the daylight windows allowing light to pour in.  The LARGE basement family room has a gorgeous wet/bar.  There is a 4th bedroom in basement along with full bath perfect for guests or additional family.  There is a cute drop zone on entry from the garage with bench & lockers that also includes the laundry area for ease of entry. The Drive way faces south perfect for keeping clean in the winter months.  There is tons of closet space and storage space throughout the home as well as the basement.  The garage has a built in ramp for 0 entry access.
